MESSAGE.value: Initial commit of HTA languages. Uses XChart for table TSV support. Mockup of the table transformation language.
Fix scope for intersection of column names.

Add column groups as an annotation on the XChart column, and support defining joins by group of columns. When a user defines an ID column group for each table, it becomes very convenient to join by ID.
Fix generation to R code. Now requires TextOutput 1.0.2 (not yet released publicly).
Add setkey on the data.table after importing it, if the table contains any column with the ID annotation.
Group setkey with the join, so that different joins can group by different columns, if needed.
inspect language: composes with TextOutput and write columns of a table to a TSV file after join, so that the new columns can be loaded and displayed after the program has run once.
Heatmap code is rendering to work. Assumes rendered table has gene id in first column, for now.
Tweak heatmap cell and font size to fit in the inspector window.
Add Prototype subset table by rows.
Calculate the Plot path rather than setting it on the property.
Prototype run configuration to run R scripts directly from MPS.
Prototype run configuration to run R scripts directly from MPS. Now invoking RScript and producing results.
Start to collect package names to assemble library statements automatically.
